{"tid":1597464,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"美國國歌香港版","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T05:04:04.000Z","uid":321468,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7eaa2172760de6cfe4d2c3f4b62148322f8ea6","tid":1597464,"uid":321468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:01:28.000Z","msg":"Oh, say can you see,<br />\n不自由，毋寧死，<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n黑衣滿城合唱，<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\n遊行歌聲遍地，<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n提着雨傘，世界動容。<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars,<br />\n假諾言，無民主，<br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n奸險濫權禍世，<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched,<br />\n沉淪卑鄙肆虐，<br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n警黑袒蔭，法理難容。<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare,<br />\n事實辦法不多，<br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n拚命全力對抗，<br />\nGave proof through the night,<br />\n天真苦與汗，<br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n垂淚甘流熱血，<br />\nOh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,<br />\n同行，那會作罷！定局！攜手，應記&hellip;<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.<br />\n尋黎明，為理想；在暗黑，於恐怖。"},{"pid":"1de368689891e8e93a45c05bcbbf2946d26423f5","tid":1597464,"uid":162268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"改人哋國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd6bb6951e47f09a29415137417f16d6f282d6a","tid":1597464,"uid":17270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8257a578adf59e1cb4d3d8ce37e7834ccc756f94","tid":1597464,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"b927e45e5d1e0c7c1837b7b300c6bd488a0e4d41","tid":1597464,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:22:14.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"24452bc1ce50113e9f7dc0dc680116ee3ab